OL,4,Ceating disorder urges NHS to act
OL,6,FA mother whose seven-year-old son died
OL,7,Fafter struggling with an undiagnosed
OL,8,Feating disorder says she fears the
OL,9,Fsame thing could happen to another
OL,10,Fchild.
OL,12,FAlfie Nicholls who had a severely
OL,13,Frestricted diet that left him
OL,14,Fmalnourished, suffered a fatal cardiac
OL,15,Farrest at home in Stockport in
OL,16,FDecember 2021.
