OL,6,FSenior Coroner Alison Mutch said it
OL,7,Fwas her job to determine from the
OL,8,Fevidence how malnutrition could
OL,9,Fcontribute to a child's death in
OL,10,F'modern Britain'.
OL,12,FLooking at the evidence she said it
OL,13,Fwas clear that the agencies involved
OL,14,Fwith Alfie did not have a clear
OL,15,Funderstanding of how much he was
OL,16,Feating.
OL,18,FLucy said she felt lighter after the
OL,19,Finquest because for years she had
OL,20,Fblamed herself.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/11
