OL,3,CMother of son who died of undiagnosed
OL,4,Ceating disorder urges NHS to act
OL,6,F"Our children should have the right to
OL,7,Fbe treated like children. If Alfie
OL,8,Fhadn't had autism, it was shown at the
OL,9,Finquest that he would have been
OL,10,Ftreated for the things he should have
OL,11,Fbeen.
OL,13,F"My son's voice should have been
OL,14,Fheard. I was his voice and I wasn't
OL,15,Fheard on several, several occasions.
OL,16,FWhen I first found out about his cause
OL,17,Fof death I thought Alfie was the only
OL,18,Fchild this has ever happened to.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/11
