OL,3,CMother of son who died of undiagnosed
OL,4,Ceating disorder urges NHS to act
OL,6,F"But now I believe there are thousands
OL,7,Fof children struggling with it. I
OL,8,Freally want to get my voice across to
OL,9,Fother parents that they are doing more
OL,10,Fthan enough. It's the system that
OL,11,Fneeds to massively change.
OL,13,F"This needs to be pushed and I don't
OL,14,Fjust mean the Stockport area, I mean
OL,15,Fnationally.
OL,17,F"Do I believe it could happen again?
OL,18,FAbsolutely. Of course it can happen
OL,19,Fagain."
