OL,6,Fis having similar problems with her
OL,7,Fson James. He eats only five 'safe
OL,8,Ffoods' and is also autistic and non-
OL,9,Fverbal like Alfie was.
OL,11,FAfter seeing Alfie's story she made
OL,12,Fthe trip up to Stockport to meet Lucy
OL,13,Fto see how they could join forces.
OL,15,F"When I read about Alfie's story and
OL,16,Fall he and Lucy went through it made
OL,17,Fmy heart stop. It shouldn't be
OL,18,Fhappening and I'll be damned if I let
OL,19,Fit happen again."
