OL,6,FA spokesperson for Stockport NHS
OL,7,FFoundation Trust which runs Stepping
OL,8,FHill Hospital, said: "Firstly, we'd
OL,9,Flike to offer our condolences again to
OL,10,FAlfie's family. Alfie's was a very
OL,11,Ftragic and complex case. We are deeply
OL,12,Fsorry for the missed opportunities
OL,13,Fidentified in our internal review and
OL,14,Fthrough the inquest process, and we
OL,15,Fexpress our sincere apologies to
OL,16,FAlfie's family.
