OL,6,F"Since this case we have introduced
OL,7,Fnew guidelines for the care and
OL,8,Fmanagement of children with a
OL,9,Frestricted diet to help ensure warning
OL,10,Fsigns can be more readily identified
OL,11,Fand acted upon, and we are glad that
OL,12,Fthe coroner is satisfied with these
OL,13,Factions."
OL,15,FNHS England also told us it that its
OL,16,Feating disorder guidance for children
OL,17,Fand young people is being updated to
OL,18,Finclude Arfid and is due to be
OL,19,Fpublished later this year.
